01:08:15.748 --> 01:08:18.316
All you need to know is that he
is here,

01:08:18.316 --> 01:08:21.189
and he is the source of your weakness,

01:08:21.189 --> 01:08:24.714
and if you can rid the world
of one more piece of shit,

01:08:24.714 --> 01:08:25.932
then you will rid the world

01:08:25.932 --> 01:08:29.327
of everything that is holding
you back!

01:08:31.068 --> 01:08:33.636
No, leave it on.

01:08:34.680 --> 01:08:36.117
