to do.

01:10:49.119 --> 01:10:52.035
Take that bat and crush it.

01:10:52.035 --> 01:10:54.255
Smash it to pieces.

01:11:10.009 --> 01:11:12.403
What are you waiting for?

01:11:13.361 --> 01:11:14.753
