01:11:20.324 --> 01:11:21.194
It's...

01:11:22.674 --> 01:11:23.501
Is that...

01:11:25.068 --> 01:11:26.287
Is that...

01:11:26.287 --> 01:11:29.507
Pick up the bat and smash it.

01:11:29.507 --> 01:11:33.511
