01:11:36.645 --> 01:11:38.951
Pick up the bat and smash it!

01:11:40.910 --> 01:11:41.693
Do it!

01:11:41.693 --> 01:11:43.304
No!

01:11:43.304 --> 01:11:45.306
Crush your fears!

01:11:45.306 --> 01:11:48.526
No!

01:11:48.526 --> 01:11:50.485
Good, Frank.

01:11:52.313 --> 01:11:53.139
Good.

01:11:58.057 --> 01:11:59.189
What's he doin' here?

01:12:01.060 --> 01:12:03.062
John here doesn't hesitate.

01:12:03.062 --> 01:12:04.281
