01:12:05.413 --> 01:12:08.285
That man is a pedophile
who needs to be punished.

01:12:14.639 --> 01:12:15.727
So what now, Frank?

01:12:16.946 --> 01:12:18.077
You made a choice.

01:12:18.948 --> 01:12:20.079
You stood up to me.

01:12:23.648 --> 01:12:28.697
I'm so sorry!

01:12:29.915 --> 01:12:31.526
I couldn't do it.

01:12:34.267 --> 01:12:36.618
I just couldn't go through with
it!

01:12:42.885 --> 01:12:44.365
Dammit, Frank!

01:12:44.365 --> 01:12:45.496
You were there!

01:12:45.496 --> 01:12:47.237
You were so close!

01:12:47.237 --> 01:12:48.194
You stood up to me!

01:12:48.194 --> 01:12:49.935
You challenged me, and then...

01:12:51.372 --> 01:12:52.808
Blew it.

01:12:52.808 --> 01:12:54.505
Get him the fuck off this earth!

01:12:55.767 --> 01:12:57.508
