01:13:03.645 --> 01:13:05.124
Lost another one, huh, Tobin?

01:13:16.353 --> 01:13:19.182
What the fuck is
going on?

01:13:19.182 --> 01:13:20.923
Lily.

01:13:20.923 --> 01:13:22.446
Oh, Lily,

01:13:22.446 --> 01:13:25.057
