01:13:44.773 --> 01:13:45.904
Shut it!

01:13:45.904 --> 01:13:47.123
You say Frank's name one more time,

01:13:47.123 --> 01:13:48.341
and I swear to god,

01:13:48.341 --> 01:13:49.342
I'll have John put a bullet in
your head,

01:13:49.342 --> 01:13:50.735
just like he did to Frank!

01:13:52.781 --> 01:13:54.130
Now, what do we have here?

01:13:56.437 --> 01:13:57.438
We have a final meal.

01:13:58.874 --> 01:14:01.790
A last supper, so to speak.

01:14:01.790 --> 01:14:03.444
What does that mean?

01:14:05.315 --> 01:14:06.577
John?

01:14:20.417 --> 01:14:23.246
What are you gonna make
me do?

01:14:23.246 --> 01:14:25.161
You're going to eat that.

01:14:25.161 --> 01:14:27.468
You're going to eat the weak.

01:14:30.471 --> 01:14:31.341
