have to have

01:14:31.341 --> 01:14:32.342
you eat some leeches,

01:14:32.342 --> 01:14:33.778
but things happened,

01:14:33.778 --> 01:14:36.302
and, well, Frank's weak,

01:14:36.302 --> 01:14:40.568
and if you eat Frank, you'll
be eating your weakness.

01:14:40.568 --> 01:14:42.178
I can't.

01:14:42.178 --> 01:14:43.832
You can and you will!

01:14:45.616 --> 01:14:46.487
No.

01:14:46.487 --> 01:14:48.489
Say yes to this.

01:14:48.489 --> 01:14:50.403
You say yes to everything else,

01:14:50.403 --> 01:14:51.796
say yes to this!

01:14:51.796 --> 01:14:54.625
No.

01:14:54.625 --> 01:14:56.497
Put the fucking skin in your
mouth!

01:14:58.586 --> 01:15:00.849
Don't any of you fucking move!

01:15:03.373 --> 01:15:06.332
Lily, pull your chair back.

01:15:09.727 --> 01:15:12.948
You're a fucking murderer, Tobin Vance.

01:15:12.948 --> 01:15:14.602
And you, too, John.

01:15:14.602 --> 01:15:16.429
Whatever the fuck your name is!

01:15:17.996 --> 01:15:20.956
I take it you're working
for Vance, too, huh?

01:15:20.956 --> 01:15:22.044
Well, guess what?

01:15:22.044 --> 01:15:23.785
You're all going to jail.

01:15:23.785 --> 01:15:26.265
I'm a police officer.

01:15:26.265 --> 01:15:28.572
That's right, dickhead!

01:15:28.572 --> 01:15:31.357
I've been documenting everything.

01:15:32.402 --> 01:15:34.404
And I've seen you fucks kill people.

01:15:35.666 --> 01:15:36.537
Twice now!

01:15:39.365 --> 01:15:40.758
You're gonna pay.

01:15:42.325 --> 01:15:44.327
Haven't we changed you, Jesse?

01:15:46.895 --> 01:15:49.114
That is a fucking joke!

01:15:50.333 --> 01:15:51.813
This whole retreat is a joke.

01:15:54.816 --> 01:15:55.643
Then shoot me.

01:15:57.862 --> 01:15:58.689
What?

01:16:00.082 --> 01:16:00.952
Shoot me.

01:16:00.952 --> 01:16:02.867
Let's see if you have the guts.

01:16:02.867 --> 01:16:03.912
Oh.

01:16:03.912 --> 01:16:05.043
Oh, I have the guts.

01:16:06.001 --> 01:16:07.437
20 years on the force.

01:16:08.569 --> 01:16:09.961
So what?

01:16:09.961 --> 01:16:11.659
You're an undercover cop?

01:16:11.659 --> 01:16:14.618
You stay the fuck out of this,
John!

01:16:14.618 --> 01:16:16.446
Had you figured out all along!

01:16:20.972 --> 01:16:23.279
