01:16:24.889 --> 01:16:28.240
No, you're gonna have
to shoot me to learn.

01:16:28.240 --> 01:16:29.328
To learn what, huh?

01:16:31.156 --> 01:16:33.289
That I can put down a piece of
shit?

01:16:33.289 --> 01:16:35.857
