01:16:35.857 --> 01:16:36.684
Do it now!

01:16:36.684 --> 01:16:38.120
Shut the fuck up!

01:16:38.120 --> 01:16:39.382
Both of you!

01:16:39.382 --> 01:16:40.862
Pull the trigger!

01:16:51.873 --> 01:16:53.135
You!

01:16:53.135 --> 01:16:55.485
You fucking bastards!

01:16:55.485 --> 01:16:58.053
