01:16:59.707 --> 01:17:00.795
Did we, Jesse,

01:17:02.448 --> 01:17:03.275
or did you?

01:17:04.494 --> 01:17:05.974
What the fuck are you talkin'
about?

01:17:07.497 --> 01:17:09.586
I'm a police officer.

01:17:09.586 --> 01:17:13.068
I've been a police officer for
20 years!

01:17:13.068 --> 01:17:14.722
You're not a cop.

01:17:14.722 --> 01:17:16.549
You're simply insane.

01:17:17.986 --> 01:17:20.118
Elizabeth.

01:17:23.556 --> 01:17:24.819
Jesse Donovan,

01:17:24.819 --> 01:17:26.603
in and out of psychiatric institutions

01:17:26.603 --> 01:17:28.039
since he was 12-years-old.

01:17:28.039 --> 01:17:31.086
Rejected by the Police Academy
six times.

01:17:31.086 --> 01:17:34.045
