impersonating an officer.

01:17:35.525 --> 01:17:36.744
But my gun?

01:17:37.875 --> 01:17:40.095
Jesse, you're not a cop.

01:17:40.095 --> 01:17:41.531
You're a nobody.

01:17:41.531 --> 01:17:43.576
You're gun has blanks in it.

01:17:43.576 --> 01:17:45.535
The same blanks you bought.

01:17:45.535 --> 01:17:48.233
No.

01:17:49.931 --> 01:17:53.021
Blanks.

01:17:54.892 --> 01:17:56.894
Still do the job this way!

01:17:58.026 --> 01:17:59.462
No, Jesse, wait!

01:18:05.947 --> 01:18:08.689
That was the first time in a
long time.

01:18:10.429 --> 01:18:13.041
