01:18:14.738 --> 01:18:15.783
And Jesse, too, huh?

01:18:18.307 --> 01:18:19.134
What's that?

01:18:20.613 --> 01:18:21.789
You just keep failing.

01:18:48.337 --> 01:18:49.207
