01:19:05.049 --> 01:19:07.530
Tobin wanted Jesse as an acolyte.

01:19:07.530 --> 01:19:08.792
Frank, too.

01:19:08.792 --> 01:19:11.273
He wanted all of them,
and he only got two.

01:19:14.015 --> 01:19:15.233
Not to mention,

01:19:15.233 --> 01:19:16.713
