Henry at the gun range.

01:19:17.975 --> 01:19:19.411
What are you saying, John?

01:19:22.414 --> 01:19:24.765
Is Tobin the man he once was?

01:19:26.767 --> 01:19:27.985
Victor?

01:19:27.985 --> 01:19:29.987
So is that what he's doing now?

01:19:31.684 --> 01:19:33.338
Creating an army?

01:19:34.426 --> 01:19:37.952
You've got a problem.

01:19:39.344 --> 01:19:41.956
You don't know how powerful you
are!

01:19:43.696 --> 01:19:44.959
But it's not your fault!

01:19:46.090 --> 01:19:47.483
