want you in the program.

01:19:55.447 --> 01:19:57.188
I'm done talking about this.

01:19:58.189 --> 01:20:00.148
I don't know shit about what
he's doing.

01:20:01.889 --> 01:20:02.759
Starting...

01:20:04.630 --> 01:20:05.936
An army.

01:20:10.071 --> 01:20:14.858
Your number one goal should
be to find your purpose!

01:20:17.556 --> 01:20:18.383
But you can't!

01:20:19.471 --> 01:20:23.301
Because first, you need
to find your enemy,

01:20:23.301 --> 01:20:25.303
identify them,

01:20:25.303 --> 01:20:27.479
so that you can rise up,

01:20:27.479 --> 01:20:28.611
and crush them!

01:20:29.960 --> 01:20:31.048
When you do that,

01:20:31.048 --> 01:20:34.530
the possibilities are endless!

01:20:34.530 --> 01:20:36.837
And you can rule the world!

01:20:40.841 --> 01:20:42.886
I said I was done talkin'
about this.

01:20:45.497 --> 01:20:47.151
And when I say I'm done, I'm
done.

01:20:48.022 --> 01:20:49.327
Got it?

01:20:49.327 --> 01:20:50.154
