01:20:51.852 --> 01:20:52.809
Got it here?

01:20:52.809 --> 01:20:53.636
Got it...

01:20:53.636 --> 01:20:54.463
Got it everywhere again.

01:20:57.640 --> 01:21:02.297
Now, let's talk about results.
